name: Stephanie Torres
coverLetter: Hello my name is Stephanie, I have been trimming for 2 years. I can trim 1-2 pounds a day of indoor cannabis. I've never trimmed outdoor but I'm willing to try it. I currently trim 5-10 days a month. I'm looking to work part time but I'm willing to work full time if available. You can contact me at (949)973-6303 for further questions.
